sequenceDiagram
  participant C as Browser
  participant G as Gateway
  participant CH as chat-service
  participant R as Redis

  C->>G: POST /api/chat/ws-ticket (Bearer JWT)
  G->>CH: (authenticated) mint ticket
  CH->>R: SET ticket -> userId:role (60s TTL)
  CH-->>C: { ticket }

  Note over C,R: the WebSocket handshake carries no auth header

  C->>CH: WS connect ?ticket=...
  CH->>R: GETDEL ticket (atomic, single-use)
  R-->>CH: userId:role
  CH-->>C: connected (identity bound to the session)
